    - **Source IPs**: `36.129.175.90`
    - **Target Ports/Services**: 5555 (ADB)
    - **Payload/Artifact Excerpts**: `pm path com.ufo.miner`

## 11. Indicators of Interest
- **CVE**: `CVE-2025-55182`
- **IP Addresses**:
